former\")\n\nFeatures:\n- Insert: O(log n) add new word [web:118][web:126]\n- Search: O(log n) find word (vs O(n) array) [web:118][web:126]\n- Sorted traversal: In-order returns alphabetically sorted vocabulary [web:119][web:126]\n- Range query: Find all words between \"ai\" and \"deep\" [web:119]\n\nBenefits:\n- Fast lookup: 100K words → O(log 100K) ≈ 17 steps (vs 100K) [web:126]\n- Sorted order: Alphabetical traversal for UI [web:119]\n- Dynamic: Add/remove words without reindexing [web:119]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Outcome"},{"type":"text","text":": 100K-word vocabulary with O(log n) search and sorted traversal."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Common Mistakes to Avoid"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mistake"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Consequence"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Fix"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Unbalanced BST"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"O(n) worst case (like linked list)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use AVL/Red-Black (self-balancing)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{